query:
UPDATE miniblocks
            SET
                fee_account_address = (
                    SELECT
                        l1_batches.fee_account_address
                    FROM
                        l1_batches
                    ORDER BY
                        l1_batches.number DESC
                    LIMIT
                        1
                )
            WHERE
                l1_batch_number IS NULL
                AND fee_account_address = 'x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000'::bytea
